treestcher.name: Cristiano Ronaldo
treestcher.description: Cristiano Ronaldo dos Santos Aveiro, couramment appelé Cristiano Ronaldo ou Ronaldo et surnommé CR7, né le 5 février 1985 à Funchal, est un footballeur international portugais qui joue au poste d'attaquant au Al-Nassr FC.

treestcher.name: Vin Diesel
treestcher.description: We focus a great deal on the understanding of behavioral psychology and influence triggers which are crucial for becoming a well-rounded Digital Marketer. We understand that theory is important to build a solid foundation, we understand that theory alone isn’t going to get the job done so that’s why this course is packed with practical hands-on examples that you can follow step by step
